sub_title: Certified Professional Coach (ICF member), English language teacher, trainer, Cambridge exams, IELTS
summary:
I help individuals, teachers and schools with Teacher Training, Cambridge English Exams and IELTS.
Teachers: be more efficient and effective in the classroom and/or integrate Cambridge into your curriculum.
Exam/Test takers: get examiner feedback on your reading, writing, speaking and listening skills and learn effective strategies to succeed.
IELTS test re-takers: With my feedback you find out where you have been going wrong and what you need to do finally ace that test !
Teachers/schools: I can help you integrate Cambridge English exams into your school syllabus and gain examiner insight in order to help your pupils succeed. 

Branwen Spence    
goodspelll@yahoo.com
